abstrac: Freelance Bookkeeper, Staff Accountant and Financial Wizard
bio:
Hello!  

You must be looking for me! Your new Accountant/Bookkeeper, I know I am getting a little ahead of myself. However; If you are in need of a financial wizard, that is so talented at the craft of crunching numbers or clerical duties that it seems like her skills must be magical; you are in the right place.   

I am an experienced accountant that has focused the majority of my career on small business clients from basic bookkeeping and tax preparation to financial advising for a company’s potential growth. My objective is provide quality work and also to increase my knowledge base and to become an integral part of the freelance community on guru. I am dedicated to my work and I have a quick turn over rate. My turn over rate is quick due to my extensive experience and my deep understanding of small entrepreneurial businesses and core accounting practices. Choosing me to execute your accounting/Bookkeeping or clerical needs is a guaranteed way of ensuring your own success.  

I hold a Business Bachelor’s degree from York University in Toronto, a Diploma in Business Administration, and a certificate in Bookkeeping. I am also a Quickbooks Pro advisor for desktop and online, a member of Chartered Professional Accountants of Canada (CPA), Certified General Accountants of Canada (CGA), Canadian Institute of Bookkeeping (CB), and Canadian Payroll Association (CPA).
